  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Season the chicken breast with salt and pepper.",
    "3. Grill the chicken breast for 5-6 minutes per side, or until it reaches an internal temperature of 165°F.",
    "4. Meanwhile, toast the banh mi bread by grilling it for 1-2 minutes or until it is lightly browned.",
    "5. Spread mayonnaise, pickle relish, and sriracha sauce on the toasted bread.",
    "6. Add the grilled chicken breast on top of the sauce.",
    "7. Top with cucumber, carrots, and cilantro.",
    "8. Serve immediately and enjoy!"
